==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One then two, two then one.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī ér èr, èr ér yī.

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[而]][[二]]，[[二]][[而]][[一]]'''

# (''idiom'') One in the same.
# (''idiom'') Two sides of the same coin.

